title: GEARCRACK.Arena-TiNYiSO
description:
GEARCRACK Arena (c) walter machado

Release On : 7 june 2014
Disk Amount/Format: 1 CD ISO
Type of Game : Action Media
Protection : Steam
GEARCRACK Arena was designed to put you under heavy fire on 2 clicks.
With no fillers you will put your strategy and reflexes to the test since
the first seconds of game. Create your gameplay style and upgrade your
favorite class. Core distorted guitars, heavy beat and 90s dark sci-fi
hue will join you on the quest of surviving 9 waves of Specters,
Marauders and SACI Sentinels. Enemies will use fuzzy logics and different
classes to try stopping you on this cyberpunk topdown arena adventure.
Game goes with the original soundtrack mp3 album to keep you rocking on
your way out.

1080p Graphics and over 9k eye candy sprites

320kbps High Quality original Industrial-metal/Cyberpunk soundtrack

Level variability to create a fresh experience on each play

True ARCADE concept

90s vibe
Burn/mount, install, play!
